WEBVTT

00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:05.096
One point eight billion
young women and young men

00:01:05.120 --> 00:01:07.640
are standing at the door of adulthood.

00:01:08.520 --> 00:01:10.256
Are they ready?

00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:12.640
Right now, too few of them are.

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:16.136
My favorite part of my job at UNICEF

00:01:16.160 --> 00:01:20.696
is a chance to talk to, meet with
and hear from young people

00:01:20.720 --> 00:01:22.656
all around the world.

00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:25.576
And they tell me
about their hopes and dreams.

00:01:25.600 --> 00:01:28.656
And they have amazing hopes and dreams

00:01:28.680 --> 00:01:31.080
for what they'll accomplish
in their lives.